{"tid":1609583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"督灰拉十幾個手足間Hotel Indigo係IHG Group","createTime":"2019-10-01T14:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T02:16:26.000Z","uid":5378,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"baad90f66b7a311cecae7964b17a51b2385636e1","tid":1609583,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:57:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ihg.com/hotelindigo/hotels/cn/zh/hong-kong/hkgin/hoteldetail\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ihg.com%2Fhotelindigo%2Fhotels%2Fcn%2Fzh%2Fhong-kong%2Fhkgin%2Fhoteldetail&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=0bc6462c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ihg.com/hotelindigo/hotels/cn/zh/hong-kong/hkgin/hoteldetail</a><br />\n係咪要諗下辦法sd去英國好 廣傳抵制 傳開呢間野"},{"pid":"6b4e62f97ec7176f5a2e3aff7a6773d56968c915","tid":1609583,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58f8289d59f55b34b7625e2e35f19873ebbe4b83","tid":1609583,"uid":283494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:23:53.000Z","msg":"IHG Group 有唔少酒店品牌。<br />\n<br />\n視乎各酒店經理的政治立場, 各酒店可以做法有唔同。<br />\n<br />\n不過篤顧客灰就聽執笠。"},{"pid":"70f0a47a3840c82bb6e1c7341b305a23d1aa4585","tid":1609583,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:29:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13146ce968d5355177313f7288df12441a9678a9","tid":1609583,"uid":182653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:36:56.000Z","msg":"Ihg group 原來咁樣做生意<br />\n寫封email比佢hq先"},{"pid":"2d6fa372e8f6f65acfd12e6a6cc20b1eeffd42f6","tid":1609583,"uid":85764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:29:09.000Z","msg":"十月一號前一個禮拜，Management 開完早會有幾個指示俾經理:<br />\n第一: 唔可以煽動任何人嘅情緒<br />\n第二: 唔可以比任何警察進入酒店範圍<br />\n第三: 如情況惡劣停車場卷閘可以放下<br />\n第四: 如果有任何人士需要救助例如釋放催淚彈後要搵地方暫避，可以開放停車場範圍比有需要人士。<br />\n<br />\n直到10月1號灣仔事件，酒店開放左停車場範圍比多名手足暫避，期間停車場卷集已放下阻隔警察與手足，之後警察知道有人入咗去避，不斷搵藉口進入，直到酒店後門曾有人出嚟嘅時候全部衝入去。<br />\n<br />\n我想話reception九成以上都係深黃，不過Management就深藍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJAguSF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJAguSF.jpg&h=0d737f33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb0b7974f1089d21f4559f92f3f93eae0ef7673b","tid":1609583,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:16:26.000Z","msg":"[戰術] 大家必需善待黃店, 先有更多店敢黃!! 創造黃經濟圈!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1611238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1611238</a>"}]}